# Cloudinary Setup (Free - no credit card required!)
# 1. Sign up at https://cloudinary.com/users/register_free
# 2. Go to Dashboard: https://cloudinary.com/console
# 3. Copy your "Cloud name" (e.g., "dxxxxxxxxxxxx")
# 4. Go to Settings → Upload → Add upload preset
#    - Name it "ao3_avatars"
#    - Signing Mode: "Unsigned"
#    - Folder: "ao3-skins"
# 5. Add values below:

NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLOUDINARY_UPLOAD_PRESET=ao3_avatars
